title: Mount Jefferson (Maine)
text: Mount Jefferson is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> in <a href="Penobscot%20County%2C%20Maine">Penobscot County</a> in the U.S. state of <a href="Maine">Maine</a>. It is south of <a href="Lee%2C%20Maine">Lee</a>. The mountain is also known as Jefferson Mountain.
